      "acceptanceCriteria": "https://uofa.net/synth/criteria/discretization-error-mrl2",
      "rationale": "Grid convergence index (GCI) study performed across three mesh refinement levels (coarse: 2.1M, medium: 5.8M, fine: 14.2M cells). GCI < 5% for hemolysis index QoI on the fine mesh. Richardson extrapolation confirms monotonic convergence. Required level 2 demands demonstrated mesh independence; achieved level 3 reflects formal GCI quantification exceeding MRL 2 requirements."
    },
