    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for Model Risk Level 2. The CFD hemolysis model is accepted for use in identifying worst-case operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The relative hemolysis index RH < 1 criterion is satisfied across all evaluated operating points. Six factors were not assessed, consistent with MRL 2 scoping. No weakeners identified.",
